CNCP v1 23095
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6833: Using v-if with v-slot directive cause unnecessary update hook",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:34.515188+00:00",
  "text": "Using v-if with v-slot directive cause unnecessary update hook\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.2.40\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nOpen the devtools to see the log messages.\n\n### What is expected?\n\nonUpdated shouldn't be called on Comp component.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nonUpdated is called on both App and Comp.\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "need guidance",
    "scope: slots",
    "scope: compiler",
    ":cake: p2-nice-to-have"
  ],
